description:
This is a 11 minute workout called '10 Min All-Out Elliptical HIIT Workout' from the channel Sunny Health & Fitness.
The workout falls under Cardio/Elliptical and Cardio/HIIT.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Beginner fitness levels.
You'll need Other for this workout.
The workout has a The Firestarter and The Warrior Workout vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Moderate and Challenging.

Original workout description: Pressed for time, but still want to achieve an effective cardiovascular workout on your elliptical? Follow along with Sunny Trainer Sydney for 10 minutes of all-out interval work on your elliptical at home. If you have time, repeat it twice for an even bigger calorie burn! 

10 Min All-Out Elliptical HIIT Workout
Workout Length: 10-Minute
Workout Level: Beginner/Intermediate
Sunny Trainer: Sydney Eaton
